Change Permissions on the directory
chmod -R 777 /mnt/pve/storage

Mount NFS Share on Proxmox
Datacenter > Storage > add > NFS 
General
    ID: Backup      #Make up name for NFS share
    Server: 10.0.0.45        #IP address of synology
    Export: pick from dropdown
    Content: Pick one

    General
    ID: Make up name for NFS share
    Server: IP address of synology
    Export: pick from dropdown
    Content: Pick one

#Configuring Mount Points for services
pct set 302 --mp1 /mnt/pve/storage/downloads/,mp=/downloads
pct set 307 --mp2 /mnt/pve/storage/media,mp=/media

